# 16. Implementation Order

## Phase 1: Core Component Architecture

Build:

```text
BaseComponent
ExecutionContext
ComponentResult
ValidationResult
ComponentRegistry
Lineage utilities
Source selectors
```

Acceptance:

```text
All components share one validation/execution/result pattern.
Registries can register and retrieve components.
Lineage metadata can be attached to outputs.
```

---

